*           unnecessary data copies                                          *
*         - 16 Bit windowed mode quality improvement, along with             *
*           ordered dithering                                                *
*         - borderless windowed mode (Flype)                                 *
*         - 24 Bit RGB ordered windowed mode support (AMMX)                  *
